name: Nāmarūpa
description: All day, all night, here we are experiencing the baton of attention being passed back and forth from bodily sensations to mental formations. It's a non-stop dance party. It's a compound universe of intricate machines. It’s a gooey, frenetic ordeal, ripe for investigation. Sound by Stephen Ramsay (@younggalaxy), animation by James Paterson (@presstube)
